com.i2group.apollo.commandservice.transport
Class CardChangeInfo

java.lang.Object
  com.i2group.apollo.commandservice.transport.CardChangeInfo

public final class CardChangeInfo
extends Object

Contains information about values on a Card that the server has created or modified during execution of a CommandList. Examples of such values include the "created" and "modified" dates of cards, as well as other date values that have been adjusted to conform with time zone rules.

Since:
1.0

getModifiedProperties

public List<ModifiedProperty> getModifiedProperties()
Gets ModifiedPropertys for non-grouped properties of the changed Card to which the server provided different values from those the client supplied.

Note: ModifiedPropertys are only returned when the data stored as a PropertyValue differs from the data supplied in the CommandList.

Returns:
See above.
Since:
3.0

getModifiedPropertyGroups

public List<ModifiedPropertyGroup> getModifiedPropertyGroups()
Gets ModifiedPropertyGroups for property groups containing properties of the changed Card to which the server provided different values from those the client supplied.

Note: ModifiedPropertyGroups are only returned when the property groups they refer to contain properties for which the data stored as a PropertyValue differs from the data supplied in the CommandList.

Returns:
See above.
Since:
3.0
